curam.util.client.view
Interface Style

All Superinterfaces:
PlugInContainer<Style>, java.io.Serializable
public interface Style
extends PlugInContainer<Style>

A plug-in container that allows renderer plug-ins to be specified to control the style of the presentation of components on a page. The components are those that are not domain-specific field components, as the Domain interface represents the container for plug-ins for those field components.
